@startuml
actor Кассир
participant ":UI" as UI
participant ":RefundController" as Controller
participant ":Ticket" as Ticket
participant ":Sale" as Sale
participant ":RefundPolicy" as Policy

Кассир -> UI: scan ticket code
UI -> Controller: findTicket(code)
Controller -> Ticket: getInfo()
Ticket --> Controller: ticket data
Controller -> Policy: checkRefundEligibility(ticket)
Policy --> Controller: eligible (true/false)

alt билет можно вернуть
    Controller -> Sale: refundTicket(ticket)
    Sale --> Controller: refund processed
    Controller -> Ticket: setStatus("refunded")
    Ticket --> Controller: ok
    Controller --> UI: showRefundSuccess()
    UI --> Кассир: билет возвращён
else билет вернуть нельзя
    Controller --> UI: showRefundDenied()
    UI --> Кассир: возврат невозможен
end
@enduml